  "description": "ColorParticle is a Pocketmine-MP Plugin for player to use colored particles.",
  "readme_markdown": "<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-colorparticle\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#colorparticle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>ColorParticle</h1>\n<p>ColorParticle is a Pocketmine-MP Plugin for player to use colored particles.</p>\n<h3>\n<a id=\"user-content--how-to-use-it-\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#-how-to-use-it-\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a> How to use it? </h3>\n<p>Command: colorparticle <br>\nGeneral-Permission: colorparticle.permission<br></p>\n<p>All-Colors-Permission: colorparticle.permission.all<br></p>\n<p>One-Color-Permission: e.g. colorparticle.permission.red or colorparticle.permission.blue<br></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/45903049/120674718-abb67f00-c494-11eb-8206-84568cc9a6d9.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/45903049/120674718-abb67f00-c494-11eb-8206-84568cc9a6d9.png\" alt=\"image\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>After clicking on a Button, you will get particle while you running with the color you choosed before.<br>\nYou can also disable your particle by Clicking at the \"Cleared Particle\" Button.</p>\n<script defer src=\"https://static.cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js/v8c78df7c7c0f484497ecbca7046644da1771523124516\" integrity=\"sha512-8DS7rgIrAmghBFwoOTujcf6D9rXvH8xm8JQ1Ja01h9QX8EzXldiszufYa4IFfKdLUKTTrnSFXLDkUEOTrZQ8Qg==\" data-cf-beacon='{\"version\":\"2024.11.0\",\"token\":\"508eb1d242ef46b690a0886422106e77\",\"r\":1,\"server_timing\":{\"name\":{\"cfCacheStatus\":true,\"cfEdge\":true,\"cfExtPri\":true,\"cfL4\":true,\"cfOrigin\":true,\"cfSpeedBrain\":true},\"location_startswith\":null}}' crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>",
